                    - -O option added, to save a url in a file;
                    - Bug removed on filters routines;
                    - All memory routines are reworked, now programs is ROCKS!
                    - Aweb script has a big improvements;
  @{b}v1.3   [26.11.99]@{ub} - Some changes to support new translator.go.com protocol;
                    - Cosmetic changes;
