@node Installation "Installation"

  @{b}Important:@{ub}
  All Arexx scripts is developed for use FTranslation client
  on C:, if you dont like copy for C:, modified all calls in
  arexx scripts.

  @{b}DOPUS 4@{ub}

  * Copy FTranslator para o C:
  * Menu Project/Configure
  * Option Buttons (chooses an empty button) 
  * Types FTranslator 
    Click New Entry 
  * Add/AmigaDOS 
  * Type C:FTranslator FILE 3 {f} 
    In Flags it Selects: 
    Output to Window
  * Set Close Delay for -1
  * Now hey only to select TXT and to click in FTranslator. :)) 

  @{b}DOPUS 5@{ub}

  * Copy FTranslator for C: 
  * Menu Listers/Edit Lister Menu 
  * Add in the Item 
  * Type FTranslator 
    Add an event to him 
  * Edit on FTranslator 
  * Add/AmigaDos 
  * Type C:FTranslator FILE 3 {f} 
    Select: 
    Output to window 
    Window close button 
  * Now hey only to select TXT and to click in FTranslator. :)) 

  @{b}SCALOS@{ub}

  * Copy FTranslator for C:
  * Start Scalos menus prefs
  * Choose a menu place
  * Click on "New Entry" button, name it Translate
  * New Command button, AmigaDOS mode
    Type C:FTranslator FILE 3 %p
  * Click on "Args WB" Checkmark
  * Save !

  @{b}A R E X X  S C R I P T S@{ub}

  @{b}FTransAMIRC.amirx for AMIRC (IRC Client)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransAMIRC.amirx for Amirc:rexx/
  * Go to Amirc Configuration
  * Create a new button
  * Name of button [Port->Eng] (example: Portugues to English)
  * /rx FTransAmirc.amirx 3 (3 is a translation direction)
  * Select text click [Port->Eng] and see! :)

  @{b}FTransAWEB.awebrx for AWEB (WWW Client)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransAWEB.awebrx to AWEB3:Plugins/
  * Go to AWeb/Settings/GUI Setting
  * Select folder AREXX
  * Click in ADD
  * Title    -> [Port->Eng] (Example: Portuguese to English)
  * Shortcut -> Choice
  * Macro    -> AWeb3:Plugins/FTransAWEB.awebrx 3 (3 is a translation direction)
  * Select text for translation
  * Go to AREXX Menu and select [Port->Eng]
  * Wait for windows with translation :)

    @{b}Other Aweb Example (Translate Current Frame in other window)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransAWEB.awebrx to AWEB3:Plugins/
  * Go to AWeb/Settings/GUI Setting
  * Select folder AREXX
  * Click in ADD
  * Title    -> Translate Current Frame (Example: Ask Direction)
  * Shortcut -> Choice
  * Macro    -> AWeb3:Plugins/FTransAWEB.awebrx X ALL (X ask about direction)
  * Go to AREXX Menu and select Translate Current Frame
  * Wait and new window will be opened with all frame translated :)

    @{b}Other Aweb Example (Translate popuplinks)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransAWEB.awebrx to AWEB3:Plugins/
  * Go to AWeb/Settings/GUI Setting
  * Select folder POPUP/Link popup menu
  * Click in ADD
  * Title    -> Translate Eng->Por (English To Portugues)
  * Command  -> AWeb3:Plugins/FTransAWEB.awebrx 3 %u (%u is a aweb url)
  * Go to AREXX Menu and select Translate Eng->Por
  * Wait and new window will be opened with all frame translated :)

  @{b}FTransYAM.rexx for YAM (E-Mail Client)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransYAM.rexx to Yam:Rexx/
  * Go to Yam Configuration
  * Select ARexx folder
  * Select 'Scripts' menu entry X
  * Name   --> Port->Eng (example: Portugues to English)
  * Script --> Yam:Rexx/FTransYam.rexx 3 mail (3 is a translation direction)
    OBS: mail    = open translation in writemail window
         request = open translation in request window
  * Select ARexx on combobox
  * Don`t select
    Open console window
    Wait for termination
  * Select text and select on menu Port->Eng and see! :)

  @{b}FTransIB.ibrx for IBROWSER (WWW Client)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransIB.ibrx to IBROWSE:IBrx/
  * Go to Preferences/General
  * Select folder Rexx
  * Click in ADD
  * Name  -> Port->Eng (Example: Portuguese to English)
  * Macro -> IBROWSE:IBrx/FTransIB.ibrx 3 (3 is a translation direction)
  * Click OK
  * Save preferences in Preferences/Save Settings
  * Select text for translation
  * Go to REXX Menu and select Port->Eng
  * Wait for windows with translation :)

  @{b}FTransFINALWRITER.rexx for FINALWRITER (text editor)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransFINALWRITER.rexx to FinalWriter:FWMacros/
  * Go to User/Other/Preferences
  * Click NEW
  * Menu Item Name Portuguese->English (This is a example)
  * Command Type, select ARexx Script
  * Click in Select and selection FTransFINALWRITER.rexx
  * PUT IN AREXX SOURCE CODE, LINE 50 NUMBER OF TRANSLATION DIRECTION
    ITS NEEDED BECAUSE FINALWRITER AREXX INTERFACE IS LIMITED
  * If like select shortcut and menu position
  * Now Save
  * Select text and click on User/Portuguese->English
  * Its open new window with translation... :)

  @{b}FTransWORDWORTH.rexx for WORDWORTH (text editor)@{ub}

  * Copy FTransWORDWORTH.rexx to WordWorth:WwRexx/
  * Go to Tools/ARexx Macros...
  * Click ADD and select FTransWORDWORTH.rexx
  * Select Close
  * Select Text
  * Go to Tools/ARexx Macros...
  * Select FTransWORDWORTH.rexx and click PLAY
  * Its open new window with translation... :)

@endnode
